It is not clear whether the partnership will specifically focus on blockchain or other technologies. The Block has reached out to Huawei for a comment and will update this story if a reply is received.<br data-v-f87c67ca="">
<br data-v-f87c67ca="">
Huawei itself is active in the blockchain space. Last year, the company<a href="https://www.huawei.com/en/press-events/news/2018/11/huawei-cloud-blockchain-service" data-v-f87c67ca=""> launched</a> a blockchain service to help global enterprises and developers create, deploy and manage blockchain applications faster and at a lower cost.&nbsp;
